	<!--==============二品法宝==============-->

	<!--储物袋-->
	<ThingDef ParentName="RI_Talisman_Base">
		<defName>RI_Talisman_StorageBag</defName>
		<label>Storage bag【Second-rate】</label>
		<description>【Second-rate】Talisman.\n\nAlthough unverifiable by reliable sources, this enchanted tool is widely recognized for its exceptional utility. Its remarkable capacity to hold much more than its own volume attracts numerous practitioners seeking its benefits. Contrary to popular belief, any storage device functions not as an interdimensional conduit but rather as a key unlocking access to specific repositories. Each container corresponds uniquely with an individual repository situated within an eternal spatial realm. According to legend, there exists a microcosm fashioned by celestial beings specifically designed for storing personal effects—referred colloquially as 'the black box world'. Rumors suggest that this enigmatic realm may even possess something akin to managerial oversight over these repositories; should complications arise due to commingling within them necessitating intervention or clearance procedures—individuals have recourse through destruction of their magical receptacle followed by complete evacuation of their repository contents if required—all powered endlessly via what's purportedly sourced from wormhole cores within 'the black box world'."</description>
		<graphicData>
			<texPath>Things/Pawn/Humanlike/Talisman/RI_Talisman_StorageBag</texPath>
		</graphicData>
		<equippedStatOffsets>
			<RI_MassCarryCapacity>30</RI_MassCarryCapacity>
			<!--30Kg偏移值-->
			<CarryingCapacity>150</CarryingCapacity>
		</equippedStatOffsets>
		<statBases>
			<Mass>0.3</Mass>
			<MarketValue>550</MarketValue>
			<MaxHitPoints>750</MaxHitPoints>
		</statBases>
		<thingSetMakerTags>
			<!--<li>RewardStandardQualitySuper</li>-->
			<li>RewardStandardLowFreq</li>
			<!--罕见任务奖励-->
		</thingSetMakerTags>
	</ThingDef>

